'''''Robin of the Wood''''' is a maze game published in 1985 for a few 8-bit computer formats by [[Odin Computer Graphics]] in the [[United Kingdom|UK]] and Serma Software in [[Spain]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://robinhoodlegend.com/video-games/|title = Robin Hood Legend| date=21 May 2011 }}</ref> It was based on the English legend of [[Robin Hood]].

